      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Prepare to be amazed by this absolute gem! This vehicle is in mint condition, looking and driving just as it did the day it left the showroom. It has been meticulously preserved, boasting a flawless finish and a pristine interior that must be seen to be believed. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly perfect example of automotive excellence!",
