    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and typical wear for its mileage. The exterior has some visible scratches and minor dings, and the interior shows signs of use, including some wear on the upholstery. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation that is still road-worthy.",
      "price": 19500.0,
