    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a major project or a source for parts. It currently has significant mechanical issues, including a non-functional transmission and an engine that requires a total rebuild. The body shows heavy rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior has sustained significant damage with torn seating and a cracked dashboard. This car is not roadworthy and will need to be towed away by the buyer; it is sold strictly as-is with no guarantees.",
      "price": 3500.0,
