    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a true showroom-quality masterpiece that functions and appears exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, protected by a custom breathable cover. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating; you will find no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections here. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule\u2014the premium leather seats remain supple and matte with absolutely no bolster wear, and the factory-fresh scent persists. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate ambient lighting, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule documented in a comprehensive service binder. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, and the original alloy wheels are free of any curb rash, wrapped in brand-new, top-tier performance tires. This is an investment-grade vehicle for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
